data.description: Beautiful Custom Rancher on 1.4 acres features a large eat in kitchen that flows into the family room and morning room.  Contains 3 bedrooms, one of which is a Primary with walk in closet and private bath.  You will also find an office and formal dining room.  The exterior features a 20 x 14 Screened porch, 2 car attached garage, shed and paved driveway.  Close proximity to the high school, dining options and shopping.
